('/works/OL121742W', 'Haunted', 'Matt Stone doesn\'t believe in ghosts. But there are those who are convinced his home, a historic Virginia estate that dates back to the Revolutionary War, is haunted. Pressured to get at the truth about some strange happenings at Melody House, he agrees to let Harrison Investigations explore the house.But he isn\'t ready for beautiful, intriguing Darcy Tremayne. As a paranormal investigator, Darcy has learned to believe in the unbelievable. And she\'s given Matt fair warning: sometimes people don\'', 'Heather Graham', 'OL8567423M', 27.99),
