('/works/OL15867391W', 'Murder Game', 'The new GhostWalker novel from the #1 New York Timesbestselling author As bodies pile up, a violent new cross-country game is blamed on the GhostWalkers. To clear their name, they infiltrate the dangerous sport. And to survive it, they must ignore the rules.\r\n\r\nGames should be fun, but for two expert teams across the country, they’re murder – because the winning team is the one that gets the most kills. The participants in this violent challenge rumored to be GhostWalkers. And Kadan Montague isn', 'Christine Feehan', 'OL24776000M', 30.99),
