('/works/OL16996964W', 'Progress in optics', 'No description', 'Emil Wolf', 'OL10260533M', 22.99),
('/works/OL17075811W', 'Sapiens', 'New York Times Bestseller\r\n\r\nA Summer Reading Pick for President Barack Obama, Bill Gates, and Mark Zuckerberg\r\n\r\nFrom a renowned historian comes a groundbreaking narrative of humanity’s creation and evolution—a #1 international bestseller—that explores the ways in which biology and history have defined us and enhanced our understanding of what it means to be “human.”\r\n\r\nOne hundred thousand years ago, at least six different species of humans inhabited Earth. Yet today there is only one—homo sap', 'Yuval Noah Harari', 'OL26234146M', 32.99),
('/works/OL17077412W', 'The Whispering Skull', 'No description', 'Jonathan Stroud', 'OL26810992M', 84.99),
('/works/OL17077942W', 'Horrorstör', 'Something strange is happening at the Orsk furniture superstore in Cleveland, Ohio. Every morning, employees arrive to find broken Kjerring bookshelves, shattered Glans water goblets, and smashed Liripip wardrobes. Sales are down, security cameras reveal nothing, and store managers are panicking.\r\n \r\nTo unravel the mystery, three employees volunteer to work a nine-hour dusk-till-dawn shift. In the dead of the night, they’ll patrol the empty showroom floor, investigate strange sights and sounds, ', 'Grady Hendrix', 'OL27295654M', 94.99),
('/works/OL1719867W', 'History of art', 'No description', 'H. W. Janson', 'OL2531764M', 70.99),
('/works/OL17200413W', 'Revival', 'In a small New England town over half a century ago, a boy is playing with his new toy soldiers in the dirt when he looks up to see a striking man, the new minister, Jamie learns later he is a man who with his beautiful wife will transform the church and the town. The men and boys are a bit in love with Mrs. Jacobs; the women and girls, with the Reverend Jacobs -- including Jamie\'s sisters and mother. Then tragedy strikes, and this charismatic preacher curses God, and is banished from the shocke', 'Stephen King', 'OL26323508M', 22.99),
('/works/OL1723736W', 'Richard Serra', 'No description', 'Richard Serra', 'OL9027407M', 9.99),
('/works/OL17308058W', 'First love', 'Runaways Axi, sixteen, and Robinson, seventeen, who met on a cancer ward, leave small-town Oregon on a cross-country trip to experience the best of life before it is too late.', 'James Patterson', 'OL29693258M', 91.99),
('/works/OL17324632W', 'The Silkworm', 'When novelist Owen Quine goes missing, his wife calls in private detective Cormoran Strike. At first, Mrs. Quine just thinks her husband has gone off by himself for a few days--as he has done before--and she wants Strike to find him and bring him home. But as Strike investigates, it becomes clear that there is more to Quine\'s disappearance than his wife realizes. The novelist has just completed a manuscript featuring poisonous pen-portraits of almost everyone he knows. If the novel were to be pu', 'J. K. Rowling', 'OL34131874M', 40.99),
('/works/OL17352669W', 'A Court of Thorns and Roses', 'When nineteen-year-old huntress Feyre kills a wolf in the woods, a terrifying creature arrives to demand retribution. Dragged to a treacherous magical land she knows about only from legends, Feyre discovers that her captor is not truly a beast, but one of the lethal, immortal faeries who once ruled her world.\r\n\r\nAt least, he\'s not a beast all the time.\r\n\r\nAs she adapts to her new home, her feelings for the faerie, Tamlin, transform from icy hostility into a fiery passion that burns through every', 'Sarah J. Maas', 'OL27099075M', 30.99),
('/works/OL1738893W', 'Arnulf Rainer', 'Seine in den 1950er Jahren entwickelten Überarbeitungen machten den 1929 in Baden bei Wien geborenen Künstler Arnulf Rainer weltweit bekannt. In Kooperation mit der Albertina in Wien würdigt das Museum Frieder Burda den international renommierten Künstler anlässlich seines 85. Geburtstages mit einer umfassenden Retrospektive, in der wesentliche Stationen seines komplexen Schaffens mit Schlüsselwerken präsentiert werden. Rainers intensive Suche nach neuen künstlerischen Wegen wie auch seine faszi', 'Arnulf Rainer', 'OL20493119M', 72.99),
('/works/OL17392581W', 'Wuthering Heights and Agnes Grey', 'Contains:\r\nAgnes Grey\r\n[Wuthering Heights](https://openlibrary.org/works/OL21177W)', 'Emily Brontë', 'OL32434572M', 36.99),
('/works/OL1742438W', 'The Tiger Who Came to Tea', 'A tiger comes to tea at Sophie\'s house and eats and drinks everything in sight, so that there is nothing left for Daddy\'s supper.', 'Judith Kerr', 'OL9909496M', 34.99),
('/works/OL1744414W', 'Fernando Botero', '194 pages : 29 cm', 'Fernando Botero', 'OL22375784M', 31.99),
('/works/OL17459314W', 'Never Been Bit', 'Read for: Paranormal romance, witches, vampires, tortured hero, angelic heroine.\r\nAlec MacQuarrie never thought he could love again, his \'heart\' was dead with his body.\r\nUntil he starts seeing Sorcha Ferguson who he has known all his life as a mature woman.\r\nShe brings light to his darkness and passion to his dead life. \r\n\r\nSorcha wanted a happy marriage to someone who would love her passionately. The answer was to obtain a Lycan of her own like her coven sisters. But she starts devepong feeling', 'Lydia Dare', 'OL26044273M', 52.99),
('/works/OL17464049W', 'In The Heat Of The Bite', 'Matthew Halkett, Earl of Blodswell, is one of the few men in the ton who can claim to be a knight in shining armor- because that\'s precisely what he was before being turned into a vampyre. When he spies a damsel in distress in the midst of a storm in Hyde Park, his natural instinct is to rush to her aid...', 'Lydia Dare', 'OL26049303M', 79.99),
('/works/OL174924W', 'Food for the family', 'No description', 'Jennie S. Wilmot', '', 93.99),
('/works/OL17520837W', 'Indigo Awakening', 'No description', 'Jordan Dane', 'OL26109756M', 32.99),
