('OL49215435M', 'The Lord of the Rings', 'When Mr. Bilbo Baggins of Bag End announced that he would shortly be celebrating his eleventy-first birthday with a party of special magnificence, there was much talk and excitement in Hobbiton.', 'J.R.R. Tolkien', 'OL21058613M', 5.99),
